data.description: Enjoy life in this beautiful tri-level home with a breakfast nook, and a master suite with a spacious walk-in closet. Dual staircases lead to a large upstairs loft, 3 additional bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms. Kitchen also comes with stainless steel appliances. Huge backyard! Enough space for a pool, hot tub, garden, and some chickens...With room to spare! Storage Shed on side of home.
